le',''),(23327,795,'_pretitle','field_62f5694fc5601'),(23328,795,'testimonials_content_title','TESTIMONIALS'),(23329,795,'_testimonials_content_title','field_61605c5dc91b2'),(23330,795,'testimonials_content_content',''),(23331,795,'_testimonials_content_content','field_61605bf9122d9'),(23332,795,'testimonials_content',''),(23333,795,'_testimonials_content','field_61605bec122d8'),(23334,795,'testimonials_0_content','As a photographer, I can say the River Bend Ranch is truly a wedding dream! It\'s the perfect venue for a wedding! Not only is the venue absolutely stunning, but the staff excel in customer experience and taking care of their clients. They put so much care and time into the venue and every wedding or event that happens there. If you are searching for a venue with a rustic aesthetics, whimsical nature, and amazing staff, the River Bend Ranch is for you.\r\n<img class=\"x1ey2m1c xds687c x5yr21d x10l6tqk x17qophe x13vifvy xh8yej3\" src=\"https://scontent-atl3-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t39.30808-6/243300363_10226781277346381_5301798274983742671_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_s600x600&amp;_nc_cat=106&amp;ccb=1-7&amp;_nc_sid=8bfeb9&amp;_nc_ohc=8oZPQGKOWBUAX9iqU_c&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-atl3-1.xx&amp;oh=00_AfD0wM_Sluh0TAn_5975r-KWCMvfqIHOTva8Tq_qFh9RxQ&amp;oe=637BED7F\" alt=\"\" />'),(23335,795,'_testimonials_0_content','field_5fce74d0375fd'),(23336,795,'testimonials_0_name','Jaime Smialek'),(23337,795,'_testimonials_0_name','field_5fce74e6375fe'),(23338,795,'testimonials_0_job_title',''),(23339,795,'_testimonials_0_job_title','field_5fce74ed375ff'),(23340,795,'testimonials_1_content','River Bend Ranch is Awesome!!!! Dan and his team are super easy to work with, and our wedding was absolutely magical. The venue is gorgeous, and requires very little of our own decorations thanks to preinstalled lighting and the beautiful setting. There was a small mix up on access time for the venue, but Dan was great and worked with us to get it all figured out. His team was there the whole time and helped make sure the vendors got all set up in the right place and that everything ran smoothly. We couldn\'t have picked a better place to get married. My brothers even got to fish in the pond while they waited for me to get ready, and several of our guests enjoyed toodling around in the peddle boats. We would absolutely recommend this venue to anyone looking to have a large event.'),(23341,795,'_testimonials_1_content','field_5fce74d0375fd'),(23342,795,'testimonials_1_name','Koby McInnis-Fuller'),(23343,795,'_testimonials_1_name','field_5fce74e6375fe'),(23344,795,'testimonials_1_job_title',''),(23345,795,'_testimonials_1_job_title','field_5fce74ed375ff'),(23346,795,'testimonials_2_content','We had our wedding at River Bend Ranch and I could not have asked for a more perfect day. Dan (the owner) made the entire planning process a breeze and had wonderful recommendations for us since we were planning our wedding from out of state. Dan and his team were incredibly helpful when the rain attempted to take over our day, but it just made it even more beautiful! The venue is absolutely breathtaking and we cannot wait to go back and stay at the cabin on site for our anniversary next year. We were able to have our rehearsal dinner at the cabin on site, our wedding on the lawn, our reception in the barn, and our morning after present opening breakfast at the cabin on site. We absolutely recommend booking this venue for any event you are considering!'),(23347,795,'_testimonials_2_content','field_5fce74d0375fd'),(23348,795,'testimonials_2_name','Shaylee Scott'),(23349,795,'_testimonials_2_name','field_5fce74e6375fe'),(23350,795,'testimonials_2_job_title',''),(23351,795,'_testimonials_2_job_title','field_5fce74ed375ff'),(23352,795,'testimonials_3_content','I have never met nicer, kinder people in a time of heartache in my life. We had my brother\'s memorial service at this absolutely wonderful, beautiful, beyond perfect place. I highly highly recommend this venue for ANY occasion.