me in your Maps application and drive right to us.\r\n\r\nOr, if you are coming from Durango, head north on Highway 550. From the City Market at 32nd Street, go about four miles up the road. Youâ€™ll see a blue highway sign for River Bend Ranch 1/2 mile, and then we are the next right turn.\r\n\r\n<iframe style=\"border: 0;\" src=\"https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3171.733771960404!2d-107.85347158469457!3d37.3488110798392!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x873ea6195c699afb%3A0x92dc9bb38fc6bcf4!2s27846%20US-550%2C%20Durango%2C%20CO%2081301!5e0!3m2!1sen!2sus!4v1668711925014!5m2!1sen!2sus\" width=\"100%\" height=\"365\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe>'),(24047,801,'_contact_section_content_right','field_637685983f17a'),(24048,801,'intro_content_icons_3_icon','792'),(24049,801,'_intro_content_icons_3_icon','field_61d75c39f93e5'),(24050,801,'intro_content_icons_3_pretitle',''),(24051,801,'_intro_content_icons_3_pretitle','field_61ddb4a3ae945'),(24052,801,'intro_content_icons_3_title','PLANNING'),(24053,801,'_intro_content_icons_3_title','field_61ddb4abae946'),(24054,801,'intro_content_icons_3_subtitle',''),(24055,801,'_intro_content_icons_3_subtitle','field_620c03690dea8'),(24056,801,'intro_content_icons_3_content','Inspired by her surroundings here in the beautiful San Juans, youâ€™ll find Brittneyâ€™s designs mimic the natural elements that are all around the four corners region. With over a decade of planning and design experience, it is the creative process of planning an event and watching it all come together that Brittney loves the most.\r\n\r\nServices offered include Planning and Design, Month-of Coordination, and custom packages to meet your needs.\r\n\r\nEvents include weddings and receptions, elopements, and corporate and family parties.'),(24057,801,'_intro_content_icons_3_content','field_61ddb4b1ae947'),(24058,801,'intro_content_icons_3_buttons','1'),(24059,801,'_intro_content_icons_3_buttons','field_61d75