view with a focus on the lake and dock in the foreground. This location not only keeps everything close to the barn, but you can have dining and cocktail tables setup outside under the lights.</p>\n<hr>\n<!-- /wp:html -->\n\n<!-- wp:html -->\n<video controls=\"\" class=\"w-100 h-auto\" poster=\"[base_url]/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/Riverbend-Ranch-Venue-Tour-Big-Willow.jpg\" src=\"\n[base_url]/wp-content/themes/insideoutcreative/videos/Venue-Tour-Big-Willow.mp4\n\"></video>\n<h2>Ceremony Site 3 - Big Willow</h2>\n<p>Everyone loves the willow trees, and ceremonies at the Big Willow are hard to beat. Nestled along the bank of our fishing pond are several trees that create an amazing setting, including opportunities for some shade.</p>\n<hr>\n<!-- /wp:html -->\n\n<!-- wp:html -->\n<video controls=\"\" class=\"w-100 h-auto\" poster=\"[base_url]/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/Riverbend-Ranch-Venue-Tour-Cabin-Willow.jpg\" src=\"\n[base_url]/wp-content/themes/insideoutcreative/videos/Venue-Tour-Cabin-Willow.mp4\n\"></video>\n<h2>Ceremony Site 4 - Cabin Willow</h2>\n<p>About 300 feet from the barn, the Cabin Willow is still a pretty easy, flat walk from the barn. See, you can have your willow tree and a big mountains view! Plus, the extra distance makes this an ideal location for arriving by horse-drawn carriage.</p>\n<hr>\n<!-- /wp:html -->\n\n<!-- wp:html -->\n<video controls=\"\" class=\"w-100 h-auto\" poster=\"[base_url]/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/Riverbend-Ranch-Venue-Tour-On-The-Dock.jpg\" src=\"\n[base_url]/wp-content/themes/insideoutcreative/videos/Venue-Tour-On-The-Dock.mp4\n\"></video>\n<h2>On the Dock</h2>\n<p>The Dock provides amazing photo opportunities, particularly at sunset; and with 360-degree views it is no wonder that everyone finds their way out there during an event. Many ceremonies have happened on the Dock, too, with guests situated along the bank of the lake.</p>\n<hr>\n<!-- /wp:html -->','Venue Tour','','publish','closed','closed','','venue-tour','','',